PRIVACY NOTICE:
This application is designed for maximum privacy. No data is collected, stored,
or transmitted to any servers beyond peer-to-peer communication. All messages
are ephemeral and destroyed when the session ends. Users are responsible for
their own security practices when using this application.

DISCLAIMER:
While this application implements zero-trace protocols and peer-to-peer
encryption, users should be aware that:
- Metadata may be visible to network observers
- Public STUN servers are used for NAT traversal
- WebRTC connections may leak local IP addresses
- For maximum security, use over VPN/Tor networks

The authors and contributors are not responsible for any misuse of this
software or any data transmitted through it.
